
# AI Application for 2030: Neural Interface Health Assistant

## Problem
Many patients with neurodegenerative diseases struggle to communicate symptoms or pain.

## AI Workflow
- **Input**: Neural signal recordings via non-invasive BCI
- **Model**: RNN/Transformer models interpret signals into health status updates
- **Output**: Translated feedback to doctors or caregivers

## Risks & Benefits
- **Benefits**: Enhances patient care, early detection of crises
- **Risks**: Privacy concerns, dependency on devices

This tech could redefine healthcare for individuals with limited mobility or speech.
